history.content: Webcasting the lecture with just slides and sound tracks is free if the lecture room has the equipments. However, webcasting with videos of the instructor is not free and is only available in certain rooms. So I would say it will be webcasted as before but whether you have the camera recording Josh Hug depends on their budget.

Hi, will CS188 be webcasted for Fall 2016? I know it's webcasted every semester but there may be budget issues. 

(I know this is a duplicate question, but a student answered the other question even though the student wasn't sure).
